<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.1">
<l>kuṉṟameṭuttu maḻaitaṭutti ḷaiyāroṭum</l>
<l>maṉṟilkuravai piṇaintamāleṉ ṉaimālceytāṉ</l>
<l>muṉṟiltaṉiniṉ ṟapeṇṇaimēl kiṭantīrkiṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṉṟiliṉkūṭṭaip pirikkakiṟpava rārkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Māl who, having lifted a mountain and blocked the rain,</l>
<l>Joined the kuravai [dance] with the girls in the commons,</l>
<l rend="indent">made me crazy!</l>
<l>Who is able to make the black ibis which, resting atop the palmyra</l>
<l>Which stands alone in the courtyard, saws at [my heart], leave its nest?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
